content.rendered:
Directed by Rikhil Bahadur.

Written by Rikhil Bahadur.

Cast Chirag Malhotra(Gaurav Aggarwal). Pranay Pachauri(Mihir Aggarwal). Kaamya Sharma(Ananya). Aditya Jain(Rohan). Vedabrata Rao(Varun). Sanya Arora(Kanika). Riya Kothari(Tanvi). Raunaq Singh Chopra(Zorawar). Shiva Dawar(Keith). Tarana Marwah(Ria). Amitabh Sharma(Pankaj Aggarwal). Geetanjali Sharma(Shobha Aggarwal). Rahul Sharma(Coach P.K.)

Language Hindi.

Producers Rikhil Bahadur. Jyoti Kapur Das. Naveen Kshatriya. Rahul Chandra Pal. Shachi Sharma.

Production Viacom18 Motion Pictures. Aexor Entertainment.
